overview:
Kenny J’s Landscaping is a fully licensed and insured landscaping company that provides design, landscape construction and landscape maintenance. Our wide range of landscape services; cleanup projects, custom water features, stone walls, pavers, and much more.

As one of Northern New Jerseys premier landscaping companies, Kenny J’s Landscaping prides itself on offering each client the professional and personal service they deserve. From the initial landscape planning through the final planting and clean up, our highly trained personnel will be there every step of the way.
